l; for us, the Kulaks, the bourgeois, the Party deviationists. At bottom, it\x{2019}s the same thing; we both reject the homo economicus of the capitalists, the egotistical, individualistic man trapped in his illusion of freedom, in favor of a homo faber: Not a self-made man but a made man, you might say in English, or a man yet to be made, since communist man must still be constructed, educated, just like your perfect National Socialist. And this man-to-be-made justifies the pitiless liquidation of everything that is uneducable, and thus justifies the NKVD and the Gestapo, gardeners of the social body, who tear out the weeds and force the good plants to follow their stakes.\x{201d} I handed him another cigarette and lit one for myself: \x{201c}You have broad ideas, for a Bolshevist politruk.\x{201d} He laughed, a little bitterly: \x{201c}That\x{2019}s because my old relations, German and otherwise, fell into disfavor. When you are sidelined, it gives you time, and especially a perspective, to reflect.\x{201d}\x{2014}\x{201c}Is that what explains why a man with your past holds such a modest position?\x{201d}\x{2014}\x{201c}No doubt. At one time, you know, I was close to Radek\x{2014}but never to Trotsky, which is why I\x{2019}m still here. But my lack of advancement doesn\x{2019}t bother me, you know. I have no personal ambition. I serve my Party and my country, and I\x{2019}m happy to die for them. But that doesn\x{2019}t keep one from thinking.\x{201d}\x{2014}\x{201c}But if you believe our two systems are identical, why are you fighting against us?\x{201d}\x{2014}\x{201c}I never said they were identical! And you\x{2019}re much too intelligent to think so. I tried to show you that the ways our ideologies function are similar. The contents, of course, differ: class and race. For me, your National Socialism is a heresy of Marxism.\x{201d}\x{2014}\x{201c}How, in your opinion, is Bolshevik ideology superior to National Socialism?\x{201d}\x{2014}\x{201c}In that it wants